{"tid":2358405,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小學常識書自我審查 刪7.1遊行內容","createTime":"2021-01-08T06:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T06:45:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2bb5a0fcbddc7ddb79667f3bf6b90ae960f22b8","tid":2358405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/HYXRXTENXBAQTDV3NGMGODCHTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FHYXRXTENXBAQTDV3NGMGODCHTI%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=8647c059\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FHYXRXTENXBAQTDV3NGMGODCHTI%2F&h=ea7137cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/HYXRXTENXBAQTDV3NGMGODCHTI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n小學常識書自我審查 刪7.1遊行內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TvoBl4JMCWuAANLnYmtlVBR-7mw=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRQAFGCE5FFETHIBRCKDJT6HDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTvoBl4JMCWuAANLnYmtlVBR-7mw%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRQAFGCE5FFETHIBRCKDJT6HDI.jpg&h=d6d0edc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【舊版】■由教育出版社出版的常識書，2019年版本仍有關於7.1遊行的描述。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港通識及中史教科書屢被揭河蟹政治內容，小學常識書不能倖免。網上流傳一本常識書截圖，最新修訂版刪去7.1大遊行相關內容。本報發現該書屬教育出版社，刪除「香港回歸紀念日活動」中7.1遊行的製圖及圖下「民間還有甚麼活動？」的思考問題，被質疑自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n內容出自教育出版社《今日常識新領域》小學三年級第六冊，在「香港知多少」部份有關「香港回歸紀念日有那些活動？」章節。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y9JuJ4gUCVhONaBaGY0da6gnJXs=/1000x493/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WOIKCJHTLBBCVHF5XKFZTUA3KY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy9JuJ4gUCVhONaBaGY0da6gnJXs%3D%2F1000x493%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWOIKCJHTLBBCVHF5XKFZTUA3KY.jpg&h=240f86aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新版】■在2020年重印兼訂正版本中，相同章節中的7.1遊行描述已被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉建源：證教界面對政治壓力<br />\n<br />\n「參考錦囊」則寫道：「每年的7月1日香港回歸紀念日，香港民間人權陣線等社會運動組織都會舉辦大型遊行，表達對當時政局的不滿」，亦列舉2003年反對23條立法、2013年促請政府實行雙普選和2019年反對逃犯條例修訂等。惟翻查最新2020年重印兼訂正版本，發現新書刪減舊版本遊行製圖，只剩下嘉年華製圖，而有關「民間還有甚麼活動？」問題亦被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n教協副會長葉建源，遊行是港人基本權利，舊版有關7.1遊行只屬事實陳述，認為新版本有此改動，或令市民質疑或因政治壓力自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人覆稱，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"36f516a13914bc54afa7829804755737a1521779","tid":2358405,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n71遊行係嗰日最重要嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n64 71<br />\n係香港人春秋二祭，不容否認"},{"pid":"11fd6f44d51a30398977c53eff799c159f02aa2f","tid":2358405,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ec34975f5d5b87e296dd2cd9921c6d0e9c3a7d","tid":2358405,"uid":7008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:30:07.000Z","msg":"因為香港已經無咗遊行權力"},{"pid":"c45e423d414b05984aa2cede7fece3320bda59f7","tid":2358405,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36f516a13914bc54afa7829804755737a1521779","tid":2358405,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n71遊行係嗰日最重要嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n64 71<br />\n係香港人春秋二祭，不容否認"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\